Gilmour Wins World Yachying Match Race Championship
TOKYO , November 15 ( Xinhua ) -- Peter Gilmour of Australia skippered Japan 's Pizza-La sailing team to beat a French boat and win the Nippon Cup world yachting match race championship on Sunday .
The Japanese team overcame a slow start to win the first two races in a best-of-three battle against the French boat , skippered by Bertrand Pace , on the final day at Hayama marina near Tokyo .
